<para id="RM0000011DD004X" category="G" type-id="3001K" name-id="SP049-05" from="200601">
<name>INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM0000011DD004X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM0000011DD004X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___00000FV00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT FRONT SHOCK ABSORBER</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Compress and extend the shock absorber rod 4 or more times.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="C132417" width="2.775699831in" height="1.771723296in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Standard</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>There is no abnormal resistance or sound and operation resistance is normal.</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<atten4>
<ptxt>If there is any abnormality, replace the front shock absorber with a new one.</ptxt>
</atten4>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
